metadata.name: Awe
metadata.description:
The beauty of simplicity is experienced by
those who have experienced peace.

Both of these qualities-peace and
simplicity are complementary.

When one is peaceful and listens to the song of nature, 
one can appreciate simplicity.

When one is simple, shedding off all the burdens
of ego, one experiences peace and appreciates
real beauty of nature and life.


Size: 2423x2423
300dpi
